"lifeSummary":"Joyce verch Llewllyn Jenkin(이)가 대략 1273년 영국 웨일스에서 태어났을 때, 그녀의 아버지 Jenkin ap Llewellyn(은)는 20세였고, 그녀의 어머니 Gwenhwfar verch Ieuan Gethyn(은)는 20세였다. 그녀는 대략 1297년 영국 잉글랜드 허퍼드실르에서 Humphrey Wever ap Ieuan(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 한 명의 아들을 두었다. 그녀는 1375년 영국 웨일스 몽고머이실르에서 103세의 나이로 사망했다."},"lv":{"circa 1273–1375":"ap 1273. gadu–1375. gads","1273–1375":"1273–1375.gads","1272–1303":"1272–1303.gads","1303–1365":"1303.gads–1365","1255–Male":"1255–miris","1255–Female":"1255–mirusi","12 December 1365":"1365. gada 12. decembris","1303":"1303. gads","circa 1273":"ap 1273. gadu","about 1303":"ap 1303. gadu","1255":"1255","1365":"1365","1375":"1375. gads","1273":"1273","1272":"1272","about 1297":"ap 1297. gadu","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Lwydiarth, Montgomershire, Wales":"Velsa, Lielbritānija","Bole House, Glovers Meaton Bradeley, Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, England","Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shropshire, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Montgomeryshire, Wales":"Montgomeryshire, Velsa, Lielbritānija"},"mg":{"circa 1273–1375":"tany ho any amin'ny 1273–1375","1273–1375":"1273–1375","1272–1303":"1272–1303","1303–1365":"1303–1365","1255–Male":"1255–Maty","1255–Female":"1255–Maty","12 December 1365":"12 desambra 1365","1303":"1303","circa 1273":"tany ho any amin'ny 1273","about 1303":"tany ho any amin'ny 1303","1255":"1255","1365":"1365","1375":"1375","1273":"1273","1272":"1272","about 1297":"tany ho any amin'ny 1297","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, Angletera, United Kingdom","Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, Angletera, United Kingdom","Lwydiarth, Montgomershire, Wales":"Pays de Galles, United Kingdom","Bole House, Glovers Meaton Bradeley, Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, England","Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shropshire, Angletera, United Kingdom","Montgomeryshire, Wales":"Montgomeryshire, Pays de Galles, United Kingdom"},"ms":{"circa 1273–1375":"kira–kira